{"tid":1722043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解取消區選反而對我地嚟講係好事 入嚟討論傾下","createTime":"2019-11-14T21:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T15:18:15.000Z","uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e85ac9f06eaa3c1f4dfc25e460bc461d40f3fd7","tid":1722043,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:22:45.000Z","msg":"直接取消區選有兩大好處:<br />\n一,<br />\n比彈藥去繼續煲民憤<br />\n<br />\n二,<br />\n其實區選真係唔樂觀,民意我地當然有,但唔好唔記得種票同老人掌心雷戰術. 到時區選一輸, 我地國際層面好難解釋.<br />\n<br />\n而且,用敵人嘅規則對抗佢 你唔覺好白痴咩?<br />\n<br />\n區選冇咗,的確我地會冇咗一個同保共黨決一死戰嘅機會,<br />\n但換嚟,係對場戰爭嘅持續. <br />\n<br />\nsor for p牌<br />\n<br />\n大家比下意見 可能我諗得唔透澈, 或者唔應該取消<br />\n歡迎大家討論下 屌我都ok"},{"pid":"7e6dbb4b0b7d0b00dcb5938245688fb68f24c735","tid":1722043,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:25:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1722021/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1722021/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f4fe960f61e0bb957fa4a74c0bf8a8522f092687","tid":1722043,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e6dbb4b0b7d0b00dcb5938245688fb68f24c735","tid":1722043,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:25:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1722021/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1722021/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:27:52.000Z","msg":"我反而係怕輸區選會令我地失去抗爭嘅大義名份,<br />\n因為選舉=民意 輸咗就等於我地冇民意<br />\n<br />\n而且係反政府示威 正常應該杯葛選舉先啱"},{"pid":"ed14fd033c726dc5298ee6cab64a03299f14fa05","tid":1722043,"uid":238748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"無工返 無車搭 邊有民意呢 我講既唔係黃絲"}]}